high_descs: Turn left walk to the end and turn left and get around the counter to in between the two stools.
Grab the cabbage that is nearest to the edge
Turn right and turn right and walk to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and put the cabbage on the first shelf, close the refrigerator
Turn left and walk to the sink
Grab the knife from the sink
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator on the left
Put the knife on the first shelf, close the refrigerator, open the refrigerator and grab the knife
Put the knife back on the first shelf, close the refrigerator
Turn around and face the kitchen island
Grab the cabbage in the middle
Turn around to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and put the cabbage on the second shelf
Grab the knife on the first shelf and slice the cabbage on the second shelf
Close the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Put cabbage in the refrigerator, use the knife to cut the cabbage

high_descs: Back up, turn around to the left, walk around the island to the very end.
Turn toward the left to face the end of the island and pick up the lettuce.
Turn around to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the lettuce on the top shelf.
Close the refrigerator, turn to the left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the solid silver knife that is in the sink basin.
Turn right and walk back to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the knife on the top shelf.
Close the refrigerator, open the refrigerator, and take the knife out.
Replace the knife into the refrigerator and close the door.
Turn around to the left and face the island.
Pick up the lettuce that is between the salt shaker and spoon
Turn around to the right to face the refrigerator.
Open the door and place the lettuce inside.
Grab the knife from the refrigerator.
Close the refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Place lettuce into a refrigerator, retrieving a cooled knife from the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left and turn around so that you can walk to the other side of the kitchen island where the barstools sit.
Pick up the lettuce that is closest to you on the right.
Turn around completely, turn left to move past the barstool, turn left again to walk past the island, and walk up to the fridge.
Place the lettuce to the right of the potato before closing the fridge door.
Turn to your left, walking forward a bit before turning right to face the kitchen sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is in the kitchen sink.
Turn to the right, walk to the end of the kitchen island, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open up the refrigerator door in front of you.
Cool off the butter knife in the fridge.
Take the butter knife out of the fridge, put it back down, and close the door.
Turn left, walk forward a few steps, then turn left again to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the middle head of lettuce that is on the island.
Turn to your left, walk to the end of the kitchen island, then left again to face the fridge.
Place the lettuce to the right of the plate in the fridge.
Take the butter knife out of the refrigerator.
Close the fridge door that is in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Move a butter knife and two heads of lettuce to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the counter, take a left at the wall towards the black chairs and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce to the far right near the edge of the counter.
Turn around to face the brown door, turn left, hang a left at the wall, go towards the white fridge, turn left and face the white fridge on your right.
Open the fridge door, place the lettuce to the right of the potato on the top shelf and close the door.
Turn left, cross the room until you reach the counter and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife from inside the sink behind the potato.
Turn right, go towards the white fridge and turn right to face the fridge.
Open the door and pull the head of lettuce towards you a little bit.
Place the knife onto the shelf in front of the lettuce, close the door to let the knife get cold, then open the door and pick up the knife.
Put the knife back down onto the top shelf in front of the lettuce and close the door.
Turn left, go towards the loaf of bread on the counter to your left side.
Pick up the head of lettuce between the salt shaker and the spoon in the middle of the counter.
Turn left, head towards the wall and turn left to face the white fridge.
Open the door and place the lettuce on the middle shelf to the right of the white plate.
Pick up the silver knife from the top shelf in front of the lettuce.
Pull the head of lettuce on the middle shelf next to the plate towards you a little bit towards the edge of the shelf and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put two heads of lettuce with a knife into the fridge.

high_descs: Walk towards the island counter
Grab a lettuce from the counter
Walk with the lettuce towards the fridge
Put the lettuce on the fridge
Walk towards the sink
Grab a knife from the sink
Walk with the knife towards the fridge
Slice the lettuce in the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge and take it again
Put the knife in the fridge
Walk towards the island counter
Take a lettuce from the counter
Walk towards the fridge with the lettuce
Put the lettuce in the fridge
Take the knife from the fridge
Slice lettuce in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put both lettuce in the fridge, slice both lettuce

high_descs: Turn left and walk around to the other side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the lettuce closest to you.
Turn around and take the lettuce to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the lettuce on the top shelf to the right of the kiwi. Close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink behind the kiwi.
Turn right and walk back to the fridge.
Open the fridge and pull the lettuce on the top shelf forward.
Place the knife horizontally on the top shelf in front of the lettuce. Close the door then open it again, then pick up the knife again.
Put the knife back down in front of the lettuce on the top shelf and close the door.
Turn around and face the kitchen island.
Pick up the lettuce to the right of the pepper on the island.
Turn around to take the lettuce to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce on the second shelf to the right of the plate.
Pick up the knife from the top shelf and adjust the lettuce on the second shelf.
Close the door of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Hold a knife in front of a closed fridge door.
